.cx/i/JfRqysC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfRqysC.png&h=9e3749c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d68c1bae81ab163920b879e7165a37f24bacaea","tid":1913001,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"係食都打包啦<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c8cb5d0a73a8d4086ab317100b3bc3ce40b2372","tid":1913001,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886f6e26c3e90ec146210c59585bbaf927f6bc58","tid":1913001,"uid":226956,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"今晚九龍灣時冰爆曬喎<br />\n<br />\n今日食咗個三眼仔 飽到嘔<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfRqysC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfRqysC.png&h=9e3749c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"咩app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5ccd8f5ddfe7b8428d9b13a40e256e036